com.jnape.palatable.lambda.traversable

Class TraversableIterable<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jnape.palatable.lambda.traversable.TraversableIterable<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the Iterable element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Functor<A,TraversableIterable>, Traversable<A,TraversableIterable>

    public final class TraversableIterable<A>
extends Object
implements Traversable<A,TraversableIterable>
    Wrap an Iterable in a Traversable such that Traversable.traverse(Function, Function) applies its computation against each element of the wrapped Iterable. Returns the result of pure if the wrapped Iterable is empty.
